内容：
- workflows: template_list类型
  - bilibili_verify模板：trigger_command, audit_group, formal_group, min_followers, timeout, verify_method等
  - keyword_filter模板：keywords, action_type, mute_duration, kick_permanently等
  - github_verify模板：min_stars, min_followers等
  - custom_approval模板：fields, approval_mode等
- blacklist: list类型，全局黑名单
- global_settings: object类型
  - enable_logging: bool
  - log_level: string (DEBUG/INFO/WARNING/ERROR)
  - max_concurrent_workflows: int
  - cleanup_interval_minutes: int
  - rate_limit_per_user: int
每个字段包含：type, description, hint, default, options（可选）